spec_data.Name: python3-defcon
spec_data.Description:
Defcon is a set of UFO (Unified Font Object) based objects optimized for use in
font editing applications. Defcon implements UFO3 as described by the UFO font
format.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 07 Oct 2017 01:07:41 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A set of flexible objects for representing UFO data
